window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The immortal Lifetree, once the source of all creation in the world, has become corrupted.</b></p> <p>Nightmarish, tainted creatures now fill the realms, and the world calls out for a hero. Nikolas, a warrior resurrected from beyond the grave, has been given the insurmountable task of destroying the evil and bringing balance to the world.</p> <p>He must win the support of four beautiful champions, learn to harness the powers they control, and fight against the chaotic hordes whose very presence chokes the life from the land itself.</p> <p>This book is perfect for fans of LitRPG and Elden Ring, and features tons of action, leveling and stats, plus unconventional relationships.</p>"; 
